metadata.name: SH01-01
metadata.description:
Unique art piece showcasing a fungus inspired universe, where nebulas resembling mushrooms float amidst stars, creating new worlds for shrooms within their solar systems.

The artwork collection features vibrant colours reminiscent of the JWST's images, creating a visually captivating fungi experience.

An unique depiction of this otherworldly landscape, transporting the viewer to an immersive and mysterious world.
